snippet.title: Astrogon - Steam release trailer
snippet.description:
-- Get the game on Steam --
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1877190/Astrogon/

-- Description --
Hardcore precision platformer, with creative mode, multiplayer versus, first competitive of the kind, with speedrun and international leaderboard. Jump and dash your way, between walls and obstacles, to reach the teleport portal.

-- Music --
Some Synthwave by JP Bianchini: https://jp.fanlink.to/some-synthwaveSynthwave Vibe by Meydän: https://linktr.ee/meydan
